## Bulk import reviews to Voxel

Bulk import reviews to Voxel:

**1\. Download plugins**

**[Download WP all import plugin \[Free version\]](https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-all-import/)**

[**Download Voxel Reviews Add-on for WP All Import**](docs.getvoxel.io_wp-content_uploads_2025_02_wpai-voxel-reviews-addon.zip_.md)

2\. Install and activate both in **WP Admin  Plugins  Add new plugin**

3\. Go to **WP Admin  All import  New import** and upload your file

4\. Select **\[Your post type\] Reviews** in the dropdown

![](data:image/png;base64,)

5\. In step 3 the available review fields for that post type are shown. Drag and drop the data from the file you uploaded to these fields

![](data:image/png;base64,)

6\. Run import
